# Built whitepapers are artefacts derived from the canonical .md source.
# Commit only when explicitly publishing a versioned PDF (e.g. tagged release
# or Zenodo deposit); otherwise let `make pdf` rebuild on demand.
*.pdf

# pandoc/LaTeX intermediate artefacts (shouldn't appear with tectonic but
# kept here defensively in case someone swaps the engine).
*.aux
*.log
*.toc
*.out
*.synctex.gz
